.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-GOSSIP" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-gossip \- show gossip graph summary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-gossip
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns node and channel counts from the local gossip graph.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"num_nodes":N,"num_channels":N,"last_timestamp":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-channel-graph (1),
.BR lightning-route-find (1)
